vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 5 to increase the service contract with Accela Inc. for the continued purchase of licenses, implementation, maintenance, and support of the building permitting and land management solution for the Department of Planning and Development - Not to exceed $413,000.00, from $9,746,786.00 to $10,159,786.00 - Financing: Data Services Fund ($400,000.00) and Building Inspection Fund ($13,000.00) (subject to annual appropriations)
